Privacy Policy for Light Browser

Last updated: [14.08.2025]

Light Browser ("we", "our", or "us") values your privacy. This application is built using MIT App Inventor and does not include any functionality for collecting, storing, or sharing user data.

1. Information We Collect

We do not collect any personal information, browsing history, search history, or usage statistics.

2. Cookies

Cookies are stored only locally on your device during your browsing session. All cookies are automatically deleted when you close the app.

3. Third-Party Services

Light Browser does not use any third-party analytics, advertising networks, or tracking tools.

4. Data Retention

Since no data is collected, there is no stored information to retain or delete.

5. Childrenâ€™s Privacy

Light Browser is suitable for general audiences and does not knowingly collect any information from children under the age of 13.

6. Changes to This Policy

Any updates to this Privacy Policy will be posted within the app description or inside the app itself.

7. Contact

